2004-11-07 15:09 UTC-0600 Vicente Guerra <vicente@guerra.com.mx>
  * source/rtl/set.c
    * Moved Unix default printer device to hb_set_SetDefaultPrinter().
    * Changed "s_HaveSetPrinterName" to "s_isDefaultPrinterDevice"
    * Minor formatting.
    * Modified the PRINTER open/close system. Centralized to be
      accesible "anywhere", respecting an output to file or the
      "real" printer, and verifying not interrupt an active
      SET PRINTER ON / SET DEVICE TO PRINTER.
      Reported by Jose Arias Vega.
  * source/rtl/console.c
    ! EJECT now can work if printer device is not already initialized.

